---

## ğŸ® Gameplay

- Press **Spacebar** on desktop or **Tap** on mobile to make the bird flap.
- Avoid the top and bottom pipes.
- Score increases every time you successfully fly through a pipe pair.
- The game ends when the bird collides or falls below the screen.
- A "Game Over" screen shows your score and high score.

